# JS SDK GenAI Instrumentation Guide

This guide defines how every GenAI provider instrumentation in the JS SDK must be implemented. The Python SDK (`sdk/python/`) is the reference. Both SDKs must emit identical telemetry.

## OTel Spec References

- Spans: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions/blob/main/docs/gen-ai/gen-ai-spans.md
- Events: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions/blob/main/docs/gen-ai/gen-ai-events.md
- Metrics: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions/blob/main/docs/gen-ai/gen-ai-metrics.md
- OpenAI-specific: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions/blob/main/docs/gen-ai/openai.md
- Anthropic-specific: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions/blob/main/docs/gen-ai/anthropic.md
- aws-bedrock-specific: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions/blob/main/docs/gen-ai/aws-bedrock.md
- Azure-specific: https://github.com/open-telemetry/semantic-conventions/blob/main/docs/gen-ai/azure-ai-inference.md

