## 10. Configuration Parameters (must match Python SDK)

| JS (camelCase) | Python (snake_case) | Default | Notes |
|----------------|---------------------|---------|-------|
| `environment` | `environment` | `"default"` | |
| `applicationName` | `application_name` | `"default"` | |
| `otlpEndpoint` | `otlp_endpoint` | `undefined` | |
| `otlpHeaders` | `otlp_headers` | `undefined` | |
| `disableBatch` | `disable_batch` | `false` | |
| `captureMessageContent` | `capture_message_content` | `true` | |
| `disabledInstrumentors` | `disabled_instrumentors` | `undefined` | |
| `disableMetrics` | `disable_metrics` | `false` | |
| `disableEvents` | `disable_events` | `false` | |
| `pricingJson` | `pricing_json` | `undefined` | |
| `maxContentLength` | `max_content_length` | `null` | |
| `customSpanAttributes` | `custom_span_attributes` | `null` | |

| JS API | Python API | Description |
|--------|-----------|-------------|
| `openlit.usingAttributes(attrs, fn)` | `openlit.using_attributes(attrs)` (context manager) | Context-scoped custom attrs |
| `openlit.injectAdditionalAttributes(fn, attrs)` | `openlit.inject_additional_attributes(fn, attrs)` | Per-call custom attrs |

