## 15. Checklist for Provider Alignment

- [ ] Span name: `{operation} {model}`
- [ ] Span kind: `CLIENT`
- [ ] 5 attributes at span creation time
- [ ] No sentinel values (no `0` for seed, no `-1` for max_tokens, no `0` for penalties)
- [ ] `error.type` on error spans
- [ ] Events emitted via LoggerProvider with span context correlation
- [ ] Events emitted independently of `captureMessageContent`
- [ ] Content attributes gated by `captureMessageContent`
- [ ] All 8 metric histograms recorded via `BaseWrapper.recordMetrics()`
- [ ] Metric `error.type` on error path
- [ ] Pricing from `OpenlitConfig.pricingInfo` (no per-call fetch)
- [ ] OTel message format for input/output messages
- [ ] Tool calls captured (name, id, args)
- [ ] Streaming: TTFT/TBT computed and recorded
- [ ] Provider-specific attributes documented and implemented
- [ ] Custom span attributes applied (global + context-scoped via `applyCustomSpanAttributes`)
- [ ] Tests updated (no `gen_ai.client.token.usage` on span, use `OpenlitConfig.pricingInfo` mock not `updatePricingJson`)
